how you that learning languages at UIC can be really fun!        YOU are: a UIC student in a French, German, Spanish, or Italian BLP course (101, 102, 103, 104) who...       Has questions about grammar, reading, writing, speaking, homework (online and on paper)  Wants tips on study strategies for our UIC language classes  Feels more comfortable talking to another student   For a SCHEDULE of French, German, Italian, Spanish tutoring click below.       Peer Tutoring Schedule      Visit us on Instagram!   Load More... Follow on Instagram           Peer Tutoring    Back to main content           What is Peer Tutoring?    Meet Our Tutors     Spanish Tutors    French Tutors    Italian Tutors    German Tutors      Tutoring Schedule (ONLINE as of 3/16)     French Tutoring Schedule    German Tutoring Schedule    Italian Tutoring Schedule    Spanish Tutoring Schedule      For Students (Tips and Resources)     Writing Resources    Reading Resources    Listening Resources    Exam Resources      Become a Tutor     Peer Tutoring Application      Peer Tutoring Blog    Tutoring FAQ    Contact Peer Tutoring             Apply to be a Peer Tutor  Are you an undergraduate student in French, German, Italian, or Spanish? See if peer tutoring is right for you!      For Students  Click here for tips and resources to enhance your language learning experience!      All About LCLC Peer Tutoring  Find out more about our tutors and our Peer Tutoring program, and spread the word to your students and colleagues!      Peer Tutoring Schedules  Find schedules for French, German, Italian, and Spanish peer tutoring times in GH 305 and GH 308.                  UIC Logo         Language  And Culture  Learning Center  College of  Liberal Arts  And  Sciences         Contact   Language and Culture Learning Center  703 South Morgan St., 301 GH Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996 2119  lclc@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu 